config BR2_PACKAGE_UNIPI_CONTROL
	bool "Unipi Control"
	select BR2_PACKAGE_UNIPI_KERNEL
	select BR2_PACKAGE_UNIPI_TOOLS
	help
	  Control Unipi I/O directly with MQTT commands and without Evok. Unipi Control use Modbus for fast access to
	  the I/O and provide MQTT topics for reading and writing the circuits. Optionally you can enable the
	  Home Assistant MQTT discovery for binary sensors, sensors, switches and covers.

	  https://https://github.com/mh-superbox/unipi-control
